TableView.name: VIEW_SMP6_EXPORTACAO_ANATEL
TableView.userDefinedSQL:
WITH dados_x_codigos AS
(SELECT c.DATA,
c.PMM,
c.CN,
c.BILHETADOR_ORIGINAL,
c.MSC,
c.CHAM_ENT60,
c.EXPURGO_TOTAL,
c.CHAM_TOT,
c.OK,
c.NOK,
c.CODIGO
FROM VIEW_MSC_VINCULO_SMP6 c,
VIEW_MSC_CN_ATIVO_SMP6 v
WHERE v.CN = c.CN
AND v.MSC = c.MSC
AND to_date(TO_CHAR(c.DATA, 'MM/yyyy'), 'MM/yyyy') = v.PERIODO
AND v.STATUS = 'T'
),
codigos_sem_dados AS
(SELECT msc,
cn
FROM
(SELECT DISTINCT primaria.msc,
primaria.cn
FROM
(SELECT DISTINCT codigo.plataforma AS msc,
codigo.cn
FROM unidade_primaria_smp6 codigo,
(SELECT DISTINCT BILHETADOR.nome
FROM indicador,
TIPO_TECNOLOGIA,
TECNOLOGIA,
BILHETADOR
WHERE TECNOLOGIA.ID_TIPO_TECNOLOGIA = indicador.ID_TIPO_TECNOLOGIA
AND TIPO_TECNOLOGIA.ID_TIPO_TECNOLOGIA = TECNOLOGIA.ID_TIPO_TECNOLOGIA
AND TECNOLOGIA.ID = BILHETADOR.ID_TECNOLOGIA
AND indicador.nome IN ('SMP6')
) bilhetador
WHERE codigo.plataforma = bilhetador.nome
) primaria,
(SELECT DISTINCT codigo.plataforma AS msc,
codigo.cn
FROM unidade_secundaria codigo,
(SELECT DISTINCT BILHETADOR.nome
FROM indicador,
TIPO_TECNOLOGIA,
TECNOLOGIA,
BILHETADOR
WHERE TECNOLOGIA.ID_TIPO_TECNOLOGIA = indicador.ID_TIPO_TECNOLOGIA
AND TIPO_TECNOLOGIA.ID_TIPO_TECNOLOGIA = TECNOLOGIA.ID_TIPO_TECNOLOGIA
AND TECNOLOGIA.ID = BILHETADOR.ID_TECNOLOGIA
AND indicador.nome IN ('SMP6')
) bilhetador
WHERE codigo.plataforma = bilhetador.nome
) secundaria
WHERE primaria.msc = secundaria.msc
AND primaria.cn = secundaria.cn
)
MINUS
SELECT DISTINCT dados_x_codigos.MSC,
TO_CHAR(dados_x_codigos.CN)
FROM dados_x_codigos
),
dados_smp6 AS
(SELECT *
FROM
(SELECT 'SMP6' AS SMP,
TO_CHAR(ddx.data, 'MM/yyyy') AS DDX,
us.codigo AS CONSOLIDACAO,
DECODE(m.codigo, NULL, 'NID', m.codigo) AS PRIMARIA,
'029' AS PONDERACAO,
NVL(TO_CHAR(SUM(NVL(OK, 0) + NVL(NOK, 0))), '-') AS val_ponderacao,
'04' AS COLETA,
'' AS indice_14,
'' AS val_indice_14,
'' AS indice_15,
'' AS val_indice_15,
'' AS indice_17,
'' AS val_indice_17,
'' AS indice_18,
'' AS val_indice_18,
'' AS indice_19,
'' AS val_indice_19,
'' AS indice_20,
'' AS val_indice_20,
'' AS indice_22,
'' AS val_indice_22,
'' AS indice_23,
'' AS val_indice_23,
'' AS indice_24,
'' AS val_indice_24,
'' AS indice_25,
'' AS val_indice_25,
'27' AS indice_27,
NVL(TO_CHAR(SUM(NVL(CHAM_ENT60, 0) + NVL(EXPURGO_TOTAL, 0))), '-') AS val_indice_27,
'28' AS indice_28,
NVL(TO_CHAR(SUM(NVL(OK, 0) + NVL(NOK, 0))), '-') AS val_indice_28,
'' AS indice_30,
'' AS val_indice_30,
'' AS indice_31,
'' AS val_indice_31,
'' AS indice_33,
'' AS val_indice_33,
'' AS indice_34,
'' AS val_indice_34,
'' AS indice_36,
'' AS val_indice_36,
'' AS indice_37,
'' AS val_indice_37
FROM
(SELECT c.*
FROM VIEW_MSC_VINCULO_SMP6 c,
VIEW_MSC_CN_ATIVO_SMP6 v
WHERE v.CN = c.CN
AND v.MSC = c.MSC
AND to_date(TO_CHAR(c.DATA, 'MM/yyyy'), 'MM/yyyy') = v.PERIODO
AND v.STATUS = 'T'
) c,
ddx ddx,
unidade_primaria_smp6 m,
unidade_secundaria us
WHERE TO_CHAR(c.DATA, 'dd/MM/yyyy') = TO_CHAR(ddx.data, 'dd/MM/yyyy')
AND c.CN = us.cn
AND c.MSC = us.plataforma
AND m.cn = us.cn
AND m.plataforma = us.plataforma
AND TRUNC(c.DATA, 'MM') >= TRUNC(m.ultima_atualizacao, 'MM')
AND TRUNC(c.DATA, 'MM') >= TRUNC(us.ultima_atualizacao, 'MM')
GROUP BY 'SMP6',
TO_CHAR(ddx.data, 'MM/yyyy'),
us.codigo,
'029',
'04',
m.codigo,
'NID'
ORDER BY CONSOLIDACAO,
PRIMARIA
)
WHERE (PRIMARIA != 'NID')
OR (CONSOLIDACAO != 'NID')
),
dados_smp6_x_sem_codigos AS
(SELECT DISTINCT d.DDX,
d.PONDERACAO,
NVL(
(SELECT codigo
FROM
(SELECT *
FROM unidade_secundaria b
ORDER BY plataforma,
c.cn,
ultima_atualizacao
) b
WHERE c.msc = b.plataforma
AND c.cn = b.cn
AND ROWNUM = 1
), 'NID') consolidacao,
NVL(
(SELECT codigo
FROM
(SELECT *
FROM unidade_primaria_smp6 b
ORDER BY plataforma,
c.cn,
ultima_atualizacao
) b
WHERE c.msc = b.plataforma
AND c.cn = b.cn
AND ROWNUM = 1
), 'NID') codigo
FROM
(SELECT DISTINCT dados_smp6.DDX, dados_smp6.PONDERACAO FROM dados_smp6
) d,
codigos_sem_dados c
),
dados_smp6_e_codigos AS
(SELECT 'SMP6' AS SMP,
dados_smp6_x_sem_codigos.DDX AS DDX,
dados_smp6_x_sem_codigos.consolidacao AS CONSOLIDACAO,
dados_smp6_x_sem_codigos.codigo AS PRIMARIA,
dados_smp6_x_sem_codigos.PONDERACAO AS PONDERACAO,
NVL(TO_CHAR(0), '-') AS val_ponderacao,
'04' AS COLETA,
'' AS indice_14,
'' AS val_indice_14,
'' AS indice_15,
'' AS val_indice_15,
'' AS indice_17,
'' AS val_indice_17,
'' AS indice_18,
'' AS val_indice_18,
'' AS indice_19,
'' AS val_indice_19,
'' AS indice_20,
'' AS val_indice_20,
'' AS indice_22,
'' AS val_indice_22,
'' AS indice_23,
'' AS val_indice_23,
'' AS indice_24,
'' AS val_indice_24,
'' AS indice_25,
'' AS val_indice_25,
'27' AS indice_27,
NVL(TO_CHAR(0), '-') AS val_indice_27,
'28' AS indice_28,
NVL(TO_CHAR(0), '-') AS val_indice_28,
'' AS indice_30,
'' AS val_indice_30,
'' AS indice_31,
'' AS val_indice_31,
'' AS indice_33,
'' AS val_indice_33,
'' AS indice_34,
'' AS val_indice_34,
'' AS indice_36,
'' AS val_indice_36,
'' AS indice_37,
'' AS val_indice_37
FROM dados_smp6_x_sem_codigos
UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM dados_smp6 ORDER BY PRIMARIA
)
SELECT dados_smp6_e_codigos.SMP,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.DDX,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.CONSOLIDACAO,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.PRIMARIA,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.PONDERACAO,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.val_ponderacao,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.COLETA,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.indice_14,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.val_indice_14,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.indice_15,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.val_indice_15,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.indice_17,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.val_indice_17,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.indice_18,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.val_indice_18,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.indice_19,

dados_smp6_e_codigos.indice_27,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.val_indice_27,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.indice_28,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.val_indice_28,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.indice_30,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.val_indice_30,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.indice_31,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.val_indice_31,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.indice_33,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.val_indice_33,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.indice_34,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.val_indice_34,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.indice_36,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.val_indice_36,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.indice_37,
dados_smp6_e_codigos.val_indice_37
FROM dados_smp6_e_codigos
